		<td><b>Famicom Z-machine</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I have been making some more progress on a Z-machine interpreter for the Famicom.<br /><br />I have posted it on the wiki at <a href="http://wiki.nesdev.com/w/index.php/User:Zzo38/Famicom_Z-machine" class="postlink">User:Zzo38/Famicom_Z-machine</a> to allow others to review the work-in-progress, as well as to use it for whatever other purpose you want to use it for.<br /><br />I continue working on it over time, and will then update the wiki after making several changes to my local copy, too.<br /><br />You are free to make a comment of it, please.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

	<table width="85%" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
